{
  "stem": "18670.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 488.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't tell me where to or what about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the first sergeant, I had to pack all my things in the two duffel bags that every soldier carries, put everything in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was pouring rain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as soon as we got outside the barracks, he said, inspection, open it up and put it down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to put all my things down in the mud.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he said, now pack it again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe I steal something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now he says 'on the double.' That means 'run.' The train is going to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're going to miss the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I have been in the Army long enough-- it was my first month, the month wasn't over yet, so I used the F word.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had nothing to lose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What can I lose now?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am being shipped out, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I walked and I made it there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the second surprise on the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the only private.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was a cadre, people that were pulled out from the 83rd Infantry Division to start a new division, the 75th Infantry Division at Fort Leonard Wood.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here I'm the only private on the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I arrived in Fort Leonard Wood and division headquarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the morning, as we fall-- fall out, they call us out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They ask who can handle a typewriter, who can do this, who can do that?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naturally, we were told before, never volunteer for anything in the Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but I found out that the softest job, the best job in the Army is a cook.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when they ask for a cook, I raise my arm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, I'm a cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
